'''第30屆哥譚獨立電影獎'''（The 30th Gotham Independent Film Awards）是{{le|獨立電影製作人計畫|Independent Filmmaker Project}}以茲獎勵[[2020年電影|2020年電影]]與電視劇的獎項，於2020年11月12日公布入圍名單<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ifp.org/press/nominations-announced-for-30th-ifp-gotham-awards/|title=Nominations Announced for 30th IFP Gotham Awards|author=Zach Mandinach|publisher={{le|獨立電影製作人計畫|Independent Filmmaker Project}}|date=2020-11-12|accessdate=2020-12-20|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208153602/https://www.ifp.org/press/nominations-announced-for-30th-ifp-gotham-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2021年1月11日宣布得獎者<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thegotham.org/press/30th-annual-ifp-gotham-awards-winners-announced/|title=30th Annual IFP Gotham Awards Winners Announced|author=Zach Mandinach|publisher=獨立電影製作人計畫|date=2021-01-11|accessdate=2021-03-14|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114195330/https://thegotham.org/press/30th-annual-ifp-gotham-awards-winners-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/01/gotham-awards-full-winners-list-live-gotham-film-and-media-institute-1234671454/|title=Gotham Awards Full Winners List: 'Nomadland', 'The Forty-Year-Old Version', 'I May Destroy You', Riz Ahmed, Nicole Beharie Among Honorees|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|author=Dino-Ray Ramos|date=2021-01-11|accessdate=2021-01-12|archive-date=2021-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210112032811/https://deadline.com/2021/01/gotham-awards-full-winners-list-live-gotham-film-and-media-institute-1234671454/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

